{"tid":1844912,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全中國確診人數增至2744宗 80人死亡","createTime":"2020-01-26T23:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T03:47:00.000Z","uid":41404,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"3680b92123cfae279e8f23bb8e5f8ca05fee08d7","tid":1844912,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T23:58:07.000Z","msg":"截至1月26日24時新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎疫情最新情況<br />\n發佈時間：2020-01-27來源：衛生應急辦公室<br />\n1月26日時0-24，30個省（區，市）報告新增確診病例769例，新增重症病例137例，新增死亡病例24例（24湖北省例）新增治愈出院病例2例，新增疑似病例3806例。<br />\n截至1月26日24時，國家衛生健康委收到30個省（區，市）累計報告確診病例2744例，現有重症病例461例，累計死亡病例80例，累計治愈出院51例。現有疑似病例5794例。<br />\n目前累計追踪到密切接觸者32799人，當日解除醫學觀察583人，現有30453人正在接受醫學觀察。"},{"pid":"93a31bf7db3a17df7af6200124ba709dba81411e","tid":1844912,"uid":264871,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T23:59:38.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】消息：武漢領導王獻良不治　成首名受感染去世官員"},{"pid":"04959b746f4b87d4765f3ce6a1b0b4cc5c750ef0","tid":1844912,"uid":60924,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:00:18.000Z","msg":"1日多700宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b32d5c6dca3838c148ab5839cfd9fbd0ef3eb3","tid":1844912,"uid":94978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc78beb4a8d9852b6fd12699fdc9950294b8d3b","tid":1844912,"uid":230416,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"04959b746f4b87d4765f3